uploadedReportFiles.error.required = Select yes, if you are uploading another file

problemWithUploadedFile.title = There is a problem with your uploaded file
problemWithUploadedFile.heading = There is a problem with your uploaded file
problemWithUploadedFile.p1 = The header rows or columns have been changed.
problemWithUploadedFile.p2 = Correct the errors then you can upload the file again, or upload a different file.
problemWithUploadedFile.p3 = Remember, do not edit the first two rows of the template, or change the order of the columns.
problemWithUploadedFile.link = Download the template file
