fileFormattingErrors.title = Your file has formatting errors
fileFormattingErrors.heading = Your file has formatting errors
fileFormattingErrors.p1 = More than 25 formatting errors have been detected in this file.
fileFormattingErrors.p2 = The errors may include things like incorrect formatting of numbers or dates, or letters in a cell that can only contain numbers.
fileFormattingErrors.p3 = These will need to be corrected before your file can be uploaded again.
fileFormattingErrors.p4 = Check the instructions in the template file for more guidance.
fileFormattingErrors.button = Back to file upload

