uploadFile.p2.preLink = Once you have
uploadFile.p2.link = downloaded the Excel template
uploadFile.p2.afterLink = and added your information, you can choose to convert it to a CSV file.
uploadFile.p3 = You must not edit the first two rows of the template, or change the order of the columns.
uploadFile.p4 = The file size must be smaller than 1GB.
uploadFile.callToAction = Continue
uploadFile.chooseFile = Choose file
uploadFile.noFileChosen = No file chosen
uploadFile.label = Upload a file
uploadFile.dropFile = or drop file
uploadFile.caption = Upload a file
