declaration.title = Declaration
declaration.heading = Declaration
declaration.p1 = By agreeing to this declaration, I confirm that:
declaration.li1 = the monthly report is a complete record of subscription events and transfers in the relevant period in relation to each account
declaration.li2 = it has been submitted on time
declaration.li3 = I understand that if my circumstances change I'll notify HM Revenue and Customs immediately
declaration.p4 = This means that you have met the reporting requirements.
declaration.button = I agree - submit

declaration.title.nilReturn = Declaration for nil report
declaration.heading.nilReturn = Declaration for nil report
declaration.p2.nilReturn = If there are no changes to all accounts held and you are submitting a nil report - you do not need to upload a file.
declaration.p3.nilReturn = You must still agree to this declaration to confirm that there are no changes.
